          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title_1": "Why Buy Directly From Hydrafacial?",
            "description_1": "<p>Hydrafacial is a professional-grade treatment powered by proprietary Vortex-Fusion™ technology, signature serum boosters and a brand that clients ask for by name. But the results and the reputation only come standard when you start with an authentic device sold directly by Hydrafacial.</p>",
            "cta_label_1": "",
            "cta_link_1": "",
            "title_2": "When you buy from us, you get:",
            "description_2": "<p></p><ul><li>A trademark license to legally promote your services as an authentic Hydrafacial treatment</li><li>A fully inspected device, tested and backed by the team who built it</li><li>Access to our proprietary serums, tips and boosters</li><li>Eligibility for warranty protection, ongoing training and clinical support</li><li>Rights to market your services as an official Hydrafacial treatment provider</li><li>A direct connection to our marketing tools and entry into our global provider network</li></ul>",
            "cta_label_2": "CTA Label",
            "cta_link_2": "",
            "image_first": false
          }
        },
        "item_7twK7K": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title_1": "3 Devices. 3 Tiers of Features. A Glow for Every Budget.",
            "description_1": "<p>Hydrafacial is a professional-grade treatment powered by proprietary Vortex-Fusion™ technology, signature serum boosters and a brand that clients ask for by name.  But the results and the reputation only come standard when you start with an authentic device sold directly by Hydrafacial.<br/><br/>No matter your practice size or budget, there’s a Hydrafacial system that delivers our signature results. Plus, you’ll enjoy the support and clinical backing that comes with buying direct.</p><ul><li><strong>Syndeo</strong> offers hands-free controls, smart features and lymphatic therapy for the most advanced Hydrafacial treatment experience.</li><li><strong>Elite</strong> and <strong>Allegro</strong> provide our proprietary Vortex-Fusion™ technology with a range of feature sets at lower price points.Looking to minimize upfront costs without compromising on support or quality? We also offer <strong>refurbished Hydrafacial devices</strong> that are fully licensed, inspected and backed by the same warranty as new devices.</li></ul>",
            "cta_label_1": "Become a Provider",
            "cta_link_1": "shopify://pages/connect-with-sales",
            "title_2": "",
            "description_2": "",
            "cta_label_2": "",
            "cta_link_2": "shopify://pages/connect-with-sales",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2.png",
            "image_first": true
          }
        },
        "item_WDy8qM": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title_1": "Why is Trademark Licensing Important?",
            "description_1": "<p>In order to be able to promote your services as a Hydrafacial treatment and order official consumables, every provider must hold a valid trademark license from Hydrafacial LLC.</p><ul><li>When you purchase a new or certified refurbished system directly from Hydrafacial, the trademark license is included.</li><li>If you purchase a device secondhand, you must pay a separate <strong>$10,000 recertification fee</strong> in order for Hydrafacial to inspect and ensure that your device is an authentic Hydrafacial device that is still safe to use on consumers. Once the device is recertified, you will be able to obtain a trademark license and use the Hydrafacial name and purchase consumables legally. </li></ul><p></p>",
            "cta_label_1": "Learn More About Provider Benefits",
            "cta_link_1": "shopify://pages/professional",
            "title_2": "Hydrafacial's Trademark Licensing:",
            "description_2": "<ul><li>Protects Your clients</li><li>Protects Your practice  </li><li>The integrity of the Hydrafacial brand, ensuring a consistent, high-quality experience every time<br/><br/>If you have already purchased a used Hydrafacial device and weren’t aware of the recertification requirement, please reach out to our Sales Support team for help.<br/><br/></li></ul>",
            "cta_label_2": "",
            "cta_link_2": "",
            "image_first": false
          }
        },
        "item_CQtbY6": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title_1": "The Cost of a “Used” Hydrafacial Machine",
            "description_1": "<p>Third-party resale devices may look like a bargain, but they leave you without the branding, support and credibility that make your investment worthwhile.</p><p><br/>Used Hydrafacial machines often arrive with unwanted surprises like outdated firmware, missing components or wear or damage that isn’t obvious until you start using it. You may not know how the device was stored, maintained or even modified.<br/><br/>Buying your device directly from Hydrafacial is the only way to ensure you’re getting a system that meets the standards and trust that define the Hydrafacial name. </p>",
            "cta_label_1": "CTA Label",
            "cta_link_1": "",
            "title_2": "",
            "description_2": "",
            "cta_label_2": "CTA Label",
            "cta_link_2": "",
